  "description": "A close-up, eye-level shot of the interior of a vibrant pink and white tulip flower. The petals curl inward, creating a circular frame around the flower's center. The center displays a dark, almost black, core, transitioning to lighter shades of purple and culminating in bright yellow anthers. The petals have delicate white edges. The background is blurred, consisting of green leaves and hints of brown tones. The lighting is soft and highlights the textures of the petals and the flower's central structure.",
